<span class="headline">More on Sullen Zek Point System</span><br>
<span class="byline">7/2/01, 9:00 PST | <a href="mailto:kwill@rpgplanet.com">Kwill</a></span><br><br>
<span class="newsitem">Absor explains in detail the point system on the deity team PvP server <a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/Forum1/HTML/000230.html" target="_top">in this thread at the Sony Developer's Corner.</a><br><br>The idea behind the point system, which tallies points for characters killed, is to be able to track players that are doing the most for their team.  Absor comments that is system was designed to encourage PvP play.</span><br><br>
